           <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Samih Al-Qasim, George Jackson, and “Enemy of the Sun”: A Poetic Spirit That Transcends Borders</h1>
      
          
    
          <div class="date-display-single">April 14, 2026</div>
    
          <div class="field-name-field-author field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix">
        <div class="field-label"><em>by</em>&nbsp;
                              <a href="/author/yousef-khanfar">Yousef Khanfar</a>
                                                                                              </div>
      </div>
    
    
    
    <div class="content pigeon-first-p">
	    <div class="pigeon-context-promotion" style="display:none;">
