    </a>
      <a href="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/6DSC_5410%20-%20Edited.jpg">
      <img src=/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/6DSC_5410%20-%20Edited.jpg class = "gaelleriaimage"  data-title="" alt="The back cover of Enemy of the Sun (1970) featuring Al-Qasim&#039;s poem in Arabic" width="570px" height="380px" >
